  "subject": "Remove amsterdam and openecomp jobs",
  "commit_message": "Remove amsterdam and openecomp jobs\n\nPer today's PTL call, we were given option to remove Amsterdam release\njobs to alleviate LF servers from having to build them. I am also removing\nthe old OpenECOMP jobs as they are not necessary anymore either.\n\nAlso, seems the docker-blessing job will not be used either. So that is\nalso removed.\n\nChange-Id: I706ec04d541925be8f04c44254379523f2085eca\nIssue-ID: POLICY-389\nSigned-off-by: Pamela Dragosh <pdragosh@research.att.com>\n",
